io.janusproject.kernel.services.jdk.logging

Class EmptyLogService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractService
      • io.janusproject.kernel.services.jdk.logging.EmptyLogService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.common.util.concurrent.Service, DependentService, LogService

    public class EmptyLogService
extends com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractService
implements LogService
    This class provides an implementation of the LogService that outputs nothing.

    This service is thread-safe.
